Package com.amazonaws.auth

Class BasicAWSCredentials

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.auth.BasicAWSCredentials
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AWSCredentials
    public class BasicAWSCredentials
extends java.lang.Object
implements AWSCredentials
    Basic implementation of the AWSCredentials interface that allows callers to pass in the AWS access key and secret access in the constructor. It is not recommended to use this class. Instead, use short term credentials from Cognito with the AWSMobileClient.
    See Also:
    AWSMobileClient
